<SYNC Start=2658114><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2658511><P Class=KRCC>
저는
<SYNC Start=2660148><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2660382><P Class=KRCC>
