- 아니야
<SYNC Start=2662793><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2662994><P Class=KRCC>
당신은 여자야
<SYNC Start=2664515><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2665896><P Class=KRCC>
