<SYNC Start=2672600><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2673510><P Class=KRCC>
타니모토 씨
<SYNC Start=2674954><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2675766><P Class=KRCC>
제게 당신은
<SYNC Start=2677795><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2680462><P Class=KRCC>
